{"tid":2098143,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"美國隊長 Chris Evans密會 灰姑娘Lily James新戀情曝光","createTime":"2020-07-07T09:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T13:40:03.000Z","uid":318316,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"96fff9a11aebd5fe03afdcef0affb2d5b2d14e3a","tid":2098143,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:17:38.000Z","msg":"39歲的「美國隊長」基斯伊雲斯（Chris Evans）近日被外媒攝得跟31歲《仙履奇緣》女主角莉莉詹絲（Lily James）秘密在酒店約會！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLily James被目睹跟基斯伊雲斯於星期五晚在倫敦的私人會所參加派對後，約於凌晨1時一同坐上的士返回基斯伊雲斯入住的Corinthia酒店，兩人分開下車更特別地以前後腳進入酒店大堂。基斯伊雲斯先從正門進了酒店，而Lily James則在酒店門外稍候，隨後見到基斯伊雲斯請職員護送她入內，不過Lily James則是走背面的另一扇門，據知外媒已詢問過雙方的經理人，但目前未得到確實回應兩人是否熱戀當中。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/494927/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7-%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E4%BC%8A%E9%9B%B2%E6%96%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%83lily-james-%E7%96%91%E6%96%B0%E6%88%80%E6%83%85%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25BD%25B1%2F494927%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%258A%25E9%2595%25B7-%25E5%259F%25BA%25E6%2596%25AF%25E4%25BC%258A%25E9%259B%25B2%25E6%2596%25AF%25E9%2585%2592%25E5%25BA%2597%25E5%25A4%259C%25E6%259C%2583lily-james-%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2588%2580%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589&d=mNwaOXjJ1pf0GC%2FIettivWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=d564100f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1/494927/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%8A%E9%95%B7-%E5%9F%BA%E6%96%AF%E4%BC%8A%E9%9B%B2%E6%96%AF%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%A4%9C%E6%9C%83lily-james-%E7%96%91%E6%96%B0%E6%88%80%E6%83%85%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89</a>"},{"pid":"9b5fd5498692922663cf7e19ce61ba33cb94081b","tid":2098143,"uid":555,"like":12,"dislike":13,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"而家先被人爆 其實好多追私frd一早知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19d3aeeaf6dd4603cd68c1f6e485e87c37fdc76","tid":2098143